Krakens04972ktp5hp4eq32wz5l85e1stgvlvm6g1cf1594232014-09-15T02:21:38ZThe Dragon Demands5014364/* In the books */[[File:Kraken.png|thumb|282px|Krakens are fearsome creatures of legend.]]
{{Quote|Kraken: strong, as long as they're in the sea.  When you take them out of the water, no bones.  They collapse under their proud weight, and slump into a heap of nothing.  You'd think they'd know that.|Ramsay Snow|The Mountain and the Viper}}
'''Krakens''' are legendary, massive cephalopods that are said to stalk the world's oceans. They are largely held to be mythical, though sailors occasionally report seeing them.

A golden Kraken on a black field is the sigil of [[House Greyjoy]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Wolf and the Lion]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
